		"name": "Chat Application API",
		"description": "A collection of requests for testing the Chat Application API.\n\nThis API demonstrates multiple communication patterns:\n- GraphQL (queries and mutations)\n- Server-Sent Events (SSE)\n- Webhooks\n- Push Notifications",
